{
  "_comment_1": "Closed vocabulary of activity_log.action values. Shared by server/routes.js (require) and src/pages/Dashboard.js (import). JSON because it loads identically in both Node and webpack without dual-module pain.",
  "_comment_2": "kind: 'signal' shows in Timeline by default. kind: 'edit' is hidden unless the user ticks Show edits.",
  "_comment_3": "When adding a new logActivity action in future features, add it here first. Backend validates against this file; Timeline reads it to decide visibility.",

